{"tid":1015674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"26歲仔為儲錢買樓　搞全裸執屋生意大受歡迎","createTime":"2019-02-10T08:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T11:07:48.000Z","uid":44725,"like":714,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"1d99fba84d9c429ff07990eff9c53861f90167ad","tid":1015674,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/02/10/bsdncw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2Fbsdncw.png&h=41430c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/02/10/50KogR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2F50KogR.png&h=649b7560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/02/10/CIne1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2FCIne1b.png&h=a305b581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/02/10/ikwpmo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F02%2F10%2Fikwpmo.png&h=c571ca64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國布賴頓一名男子有天忽發其想，希望創立一門裸體執屋生意，赤條條為客人打理家頭細務，時薪30英鎊（約305港元），僅開始兩周已大受歡迎。他近日接受傳媒訪問時透露，原來他不惜赤裸身軀、僅戴一對膠手套工作，只為早日儲錢買樓。 <br />\n<br />\n26歲艾特肯（Daniel Aitken）曾任建築工人，兩周前向家人開玩笑，稱要開創裸體清潔生意，他更坐言起行。他表示：「過去一周已為6個家庭清潔，雖然是裸體工作，但不覺得尷尬，我挺自信。」他補充，顧客當中有男有女，多數是中年人士。 <br />\n<br />\n有朋友曾取笑艾特肯，但他表示會保持專業，確保客人的居所一塵不染。同時他亦推出擁抱服務，為讓人感到受陪伴，但他強調會穿上衣服才擁抱。他希望未來數年能夠賺到足夠的錢，打造屬於自己的家。"},{"pid":"088d963db1aa7cae958e6548971d6d66f5ff5056","tid":1015674,"uid":81569,"like":258,"dislike":7,"score":251,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"港男唔試下？"},{"pid":"33b0d6e829fed444f29374eccc166267555b2e8a","tid":1015674,"uid":127991,"like":560,"dislike":7,"score":553,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:10:56.000Z","msg":"黎香港時薪1000都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji